items.badge_description: It’s been a long week and you deserve a drink, or five. Besides, isn’t that what your check is for?

It's time to give bottle shops some love by adding them as your purchased location. That's 5 check-ins with a purchased location! Tag 5 more to get to Level 2. Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
It may not be cloudy outside, but your brew definitely is! That’s at least 5 different hefeweizens. Try 5 more to unlock Level 2.

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 50 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 11!

Even the vikings had to take a break from marauding once in a while. We like to think that, like us, they enjoy relaxing with a brew from their homeland. That's 10 different beers from a brewery from Norway. Try 5 more for Level 3!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 430 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 87!

items.badge_description: At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 155 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 32! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

If your mash uses more than 50% wheat, you’ve got yourself a wheat beer. This diverse family includes goses, hefeweizens, American wheat ales, and more! That's 10 different beers in the "Wheat" category! Try 5 more for Level 3!

Hiking, fishing, swimming - there are so many wonderful things to do while you enjoy the great outdoors. Even beer is better when surrounded by the beauty of nature. That's 45 different venues categorized as Great Outdoors. Visit 5 more for Level 10!
